description: This source file initializes the React application by rendering the main App component into the DOM element with ID 'root'. It imports necessary modules including React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the App component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root to manage the React component tree for the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the specified React element into the root, initiating the React component tree rendering process.
